WEBVTT

00:02.080 --> 00:03.680
No one ever calls our landline.

00:03.680 --> 00:04.720
[narrator]
Previously on Queen Sugar...

00:04.720 --> 00:06.080
-What?
-Mom, what is it?

00:06.080 --> 00:09.000
-No. No, no, no!
-Mom.

00:09.000 --> 00:10.480
The mill's on fire.

00:12.880 --> 00:14.080
Oh, my God.

00:14.080 --> 00:15.120
I'm gonna get through this.

00:15.120 --> 00:17.280
I am still strong.

00:17.280 --> 00:19.920
-What happened?
-I found 20 bags in your
worker's car over there.

00:19.920 --> 00:21.880
You forgot I got cameras
all around this place, huh?

00:21.880 --> 00:24.080
You been checking those cameras?
Making sure they're working?

00:24.080 --> 00:25.840
-Nova?
-Calvin.

00:25.840 --> 00:27.320
Our goodbye
didn't feel right...

00:27.320 --> 00:28.680
so I thought
we should do it again

00:28.680 --> 00:30.000
or not do it at all.

00:31.280 --> 00:33.280
-[siren blaring]
-[dispatch radio chatter]

01:16.160 --> 01:17.160
Micah!

01:17.160 --> 01:18.160
Micah!

01:22.640 --> 01:24.680
I've been trying
to reach you.

01:24.680 --> 01:25.800
I'm fine. I'm sorry.

01:25.800 --> 01:27.600
We've been here
all night.

01:27.600 --> 01:30.000
-Ma'am, you can't go in.
-[Nova] She's my sister. Please.

